        "1660902144f70e2795-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>August Berg's story and brand ethos resonate positively with me. It sends the timely and important message of making conscious choices with our time, for ourselves and the world around us\", says Magnus Joergensen. ​<\/p><p>Magnus's portfolio includes Creative Director for Rosendahl Design Group on Holmegaard, Arne Jacobsen, and Kay Bojesen brands. In addition, Magnus has also worked as the Design Developer for Republic of Fritz Hansen, a renowned Danish furniture design company, all of which attained commercial success, design recognition, as well as prestigious awards.<\/p>",
            "enlarge_text": false
          }
        }
      },
